data.description: Stunning townhome in one of Mt. Pleasant's most sought-after neighborhoods in the Dunes West Community, offering a bright and meticulously maintained ''paired'' home in The Gates of Dunes West.An elegant open floor plan - Conveniently situated on the ground floor, you have one of the three bedrooms, that boasts an ensuite bathroom that doubles as a powder room for guests. Step into the kitchen adorned with custom white cabinets and granite countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cheerful and bright dining area, alongside a pantry and laundry space. Downstairs you also have attractive and easy-to-clean engineered hardwood flooring! Adding to the charm is a lovely screened in porch, leading to the fenced backyard and the picturesque, peaceful woods behind the property.Stunning townhome in one of Mt. Pleasant's most sought-after neighborhoods in the Dunes West Community, offering a bright and meticulously maintained "paired" home in The Gates of Dunes West.  An elegant open floor plan - Conveniently situated on the ground floor, you have one of the three bedrooms, that boasts an ensuite bathroom that doubles as a powder room for guests. Step into the kitchen adorned with custom white cabinets and granite countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cheerful and bright dining area, alongside a pantry and laundry space. Downstairs you also have attractive and easy-to-clean engineered hardwood flooring!  Adding to the charm is a lovely screened in porch, leading to the fenced backyard and the picturesque, peaceful woods behind the property. Providing an ideal setting for time with family or entertaining guests. Upstairs, two additional bedrooms share a generously sized full bath. The sellers also added an extended driveway so there is ample off street parking. Across the street you have the community green space and easy access to the pond!  -Golf, tennis, and swim memberships are available at the Dunes West Club nearby for an additional fee. -If boating is your passion, Wando River Marina is 4 minutes away, offering river access, boat slips and boat storage. -Spacious front porch allows plenty of space for you to relax outside and greet your guests! -Quarterly HOA fees include yard maintenance (outside of the fence.) Enjoy the open HOA greenspace across the street with pond access!                                                                                                -Downtown Charleston is only 24 minutes away -Charleston International Airport is only 24 minutes away                                                                       -The beaches of Sullivan's Island and Isle of Palms are only 18 minutes away -Roper St. Francis Hospital is only 11 minutes away
